Inspector

What is it?
===========
The qooxdoo inspector is a tool designed to help debugging qooxdoo applications. 
It consists of four seperate windows.
1. the object finder which shows a table of all qooxdoo objects.
2. the widget finder which sows a tree structure of the ui.
3. the property editor which shows all properties of the current selected object.
4. a javascript shell.


How to use it?
==============
The inspector consist of four windows which can be opened with the following key combination:
CTRL + ALT + O opens the Object finder window
CTRL + ALT + W opens the widget finder window
CTRL + ALT + P opens the property editor window
CTRL + ALT + S opens the shell

!!! ATTENTION !!!
=================
The current version of the inspector only runs in Firefox.
